name: SRI JAGANNATH MANAV SEVA SAMITI
briefDescription: SRI JAGANNATH MANAV SEVA SAMITI was incorporated on 31-10-2011 with mission for extending Healthcare specially ENT related diseases and Hearing impairment. The medical camps are arranged every week on SUNDAY within reach of KOTA (Rajasthan) and also adjoining places in Madhya Pradesh.Since 8-Jan-2012 In last 5 years approx. 50,000 (average 200 in each camp)patients are given medical help with the help of One MS/DNB Dr VINEET JAIN and his Para-medical staff of 4   (On demand the document of each camp collected in folder shall be presented with Newspaper cutting.
